args: What sort of business do you have in mind\nfor today, Prince {player_name}?
Well, you've been teaching us a lot about\nHinomoto so far.
So I was thinking it was time for us\nto show you something about Alberia.
Is there anything you want to know?
My, what a wonderful proposal.\nHmm, let me see...
As it is my duty to protect my master,\nI would know more of your martial arts.
Perhaps you might arrange a sparring\nmatch with one of your fighters?
In truth, I have been wanting to test my\nskills against your own for some time.
Looks like we've got a match.\nCleo, can you referee?
Of course. Let us adjourn to the courtyard.
S-she's so fast... I cannot evade!
Your defense is impressive, but you\ncannot win by defending forever!
Now try this on for size...\nHallowed Waters!
Elisanne looks to be in command of\nthings at the moment.
Yep. Sazanka is pretty handy with that\naxe of hers, but I bet I know how this\none's gonna end.
Elisanne's got her on the run.\nOnly a matter of time now.
Alberian martial arts...have such fierce \nand valiant attacks...
A Paladyn's skills are not for show!
Oh, they are admirable indeed...\nBut now I've seen them all!
Uh oh. Look how Sazanka's movin' now!
She's dodging the attacks instead of\nblocking them. But why?
Rgh! Don't tell me you were defending\nthis whole time just so you could\nanalyze my lancework!
Ah, I see you have caught on...\nBut it is too late!
You should have kept your wits about you!
I yield. You have bested me.
Only just; you were near to overwhelming\nme while I was still on the defensive.
Your strength is true, Sazanka.\nMight I ask you something?
What made you want to be so strong?
For my sake, I have an infinite well of\npower devoted to keeping my friends safe.
Is it the same for you? Did you grow\nstronger in order to protect your master?
No. I am a weapon for Master Ieyasu.
Superior weapons must retain a keen\nedge no matter the circumstance.
I am a weapon suitable for Master Ieyasu;\none he is not ashamed to have.
If there is a reason for my strength,\nthat is it.
So that is what makes you strong...
I would learn such formidable resolve\nif you would teach me.
And I would learn more of your own\nfighting style as well!
It has a brilliance that is enchanting.
More of that cultural exchange stuff, eh?\nMaybe you two'll even come up with some\nnew tricks!
I think I understand what Sazanka's\nfighting style is about now.
It's a way to see through an opponent's\ntechniques in order to defeat them;\na way to turn yourself INTO a weapon!
